name: World Business Press Online
overview:
WBP Online is an independent news agency established in 2005. Our scope of business ranges from market moving financial news to more general news like sports, entertainment and technology. Our main focus, however, is economic and political news.

Since day one, our mission is to bring market data, news and analytics to a global client base. We have dedicated journalists in major financial cities around the world who contribute to our website and proprietary terminals to ensure that our news is relevant and our delivery is efficient.

Our main products are the WBP Business Terminal, Flash Economic-Calendar (F-ECO), Direct News Feed (DN-Feed) and our state-of-the-art website.

With all of our products, we strive to be relevant and quick in providing the most comprehensive market news, data and analytics.
